"=== vimfx ===
noremap x :tabclose<CR>
noremap X :tabclose -select left<CR>
noremap H gT
noremap L gt
noremap gL :tabm<Space>+1<Return>
noremap gH :tabm<Space>-1<Return>
"=== firefox 默认 ===
noremap <C-f> i<C-f>
"=== 插入模式 ===
inoremap <C-a> <Insert><C-a><Insert>
