command! wiki tabopen https://www.wikipedia.org/
command! scholar tabopen http://scholar.glgoo.org/
noremap sb :baidu<Return> 
noremap sg :google<Return>
noremap sw :wiki<Return>
noremap ss :scholar<Return>
